.TH GILDER-CONVERT 1 "2026-06-18" "Gilder" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
gilder-convert \- convert and pack Gilder wallpaper packages
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B gilder-convert pack
.I source.gwpdir dest.gwp
.br
.B gilder-convert unpack
.I source.gwp dest.gwpdir
.br
.B gilder-convert wallpaper-engine
.I source-project-dir dest.gwpdir
.br
.B gilder-convert wallpaper-engine --pack
.I source-project-dir dest.gwp
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B gilder-convert
packs and unpacks Gilder wallpaper packages and converts local Wallpaper Engine
projects into Gilder packages.
.PP
Wallpaper Engine conversion currently supports static image, video, and web
projects. Scene and executable application projects are reported clearly in
.I metadata/conversion-report.json
and are not executed.
.SH OUTPUT
Converted projects contain
.I manifest.gilder.json
plus copied assets, previews, and metadata. Missing previews are generated from
static source images when possible; video projects without previews receive a
metadata-based SVG fallback until first-frame extraction is implemented.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR gilderd (1),
.BR gilderctl (1)
